import React from 'react'; import './CombinedTicket.scss'; const CombinedTicket : React.FC = props => { return (
Combined ticket to the main archaeological sites of Athens Cost: 30€

Duration: 5 days

One entry per site

Free admission days: Mar 6, Apr 18, May 18, last week-end of Sep, October 28, first Sun of Nov-Mar

Closing days: Jan 1, March 25, Good Friday Morning (open at 12:00), Easter Sunday, May 1, Dec 25, Dec 26

Opening times: Mon - Sun 8:00 - 20:00, last admission 19:30

Online tickets: etickets.tap.gr

Archaeological sites Single entry price
Acropolis 20€
Ancient Agora 10€
Roman Agora 8€
Hadrian's library 6€
Olympieion 8€
Kerameikos 8€
Aristotle's Lykeion 4€
); } export default CombinedTicket;
